{"type": "article", "id": 7354, "title": "USB 线材收纳器", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-13T07:22:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052343393Z5M1GH6pevrwliI.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tUSB 数据线整理器是桌面整理控们不可缺少的物品，普通的线材收纳大多为塑料材质，比如 Bluelounge Sumo 和 Cableanchor 的一系列作品。现在 OhYeahStudio 和 NokoAnna 试图给让线材收纳器变的更好玩儿一点儿。这个设计很简单，一个正方体大理石搁在一个铜制底板上面，中间的两条小孔容电线穿过。石头的材质给了普通的线材收纳桌面装饰功能，变的有意思了许多。但有些遗憾的是，这款产品现在还处于概念阶段，没有销售渠道。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234337TzG9rsFdoXI2P3jO.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.86716259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234337cBtOeSgrAWmXTMbI.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052343383SKdjcpmPQYtTiB0.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052343385NHo0jFOxmA6UhfT.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234338dbYDtT761pKcJESj.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}